creator: Ragha Studios
descriptionHtml:
Diwali Firecracker Indian Game is a free to play 2D hypercasual Diwali, Firecracker, colorful game with lots of exciting crackers and fireworks to celebrate. Light up the night in this explosive Diwali Firecracker celebration.
Diwali is joyous Festival of Lights and Diwali Firecracker Indian is Frenzy Game. Burst vibrant color diyas, dazzling fireworks, and take heart-pounding challenges, this game is the ultimate way to experience the awful colors and magical Diwali !

⭐⭐FEATURES⭐⭐

🧨Firecracker Showcase:
Ignite a dazzling array of fireworks, from colorful sparkling sparklers to thundering chatais, and watch the night sky come alive with a breathtaking display of magical light and color.

⭐Challenges:
Master the art of timing and precision as you navigate through a variety of firecracker challenges. Can you light them all up in time and break the top record ?

🪔 Mesmerizing Diwali-themed Environments:
Explore beautifully designed Diwali landscapes, from serene temples to vibrant marketplaces and all adorned with festive decorations that teleport you straight into the heart of the celebration.

🏆 Spread your top score with Joy:
Share your Diwali celebrations and highscore with the world! Capture and share screenshots of most spectacular/colorful firecracker and display it with friends on social media.

🎇 Tons of exciting fireworks to explode like Fountain, Catherine wheel, barrage cracker, Sparklers, etc. Unlock new rockets from the in-game shop.

Join us to celebrate the Festival of Lights and experience the magic of Diwali like never before! Download "Diwali Firecracker Indian Game" now and let the fireworks begin 🎇

Diwali Firecracker Indian Game is a game with full of fun, joy and happiness by exploding different types of crackers.
While using this Diwali Firecracker Game app, It will be a mind blowing feel like blasting crackers in real time.

The game features realistic graphics and sound effects, making it feel like you're really lighting up fireworks in your own backyard. You can also compete with your friends and family to see who can create the most impressive display.

It has easy-to-use interface and amazing gameplay, "Diwali Firecracker Indian Game" is the perfect way to celebrate the festival of lights. So light up night sky with your favorite virtual firecrackers and enjoy the festivities of Diwali in a safe and fun way!

This Game is of diwali fireworks crackers in which you will get experience of celebrating Diwali Festival and also Like Happy New Year.

HOW TO PLAY?
🔥 Control various rockets with your mouse pointer.
🔥 Dodge multiple obstacles and burst Diwali crackers.
🔥 Touch and fire up various fireworks to create a High Score.

This Diwali, New Year and Christmas download the most exciting game and make your Diwali, Christmas and New Year even brighter.
